Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "plate": "ABC-1234",
  "model": "Honda Civic EX",
  "year": 2022,
  "color": "Preto Metálico",
  "clientId": 1
}

### 12. Deletar veículo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

